gameObjects.hint: Pick up the two green bricks in front of the trashcan and move them out of the way.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Junkbot can step up and down one brick.  Move the blue brick to make a step up to the trashcan.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Put bricks under or over other bricks to build bridges. Try sticking the yellow bricks under the grey ones.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Grab the yellow stairs by the bottom brick and try moving them all at once.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Use the green bricks to make bridges just like the one in the center.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Pick up one of the white columns from the bottom. Now stack one cubicle on top of another to make a bridge.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Try building one brick at a time. Build out from the center column as well as from both sides.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Get Junkbot to the center of the room. Then build a shield like the one on the left over the right pipes.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: You can move clumps of bricks at once to save moves.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Build another bridge like the one over the first gearbot.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Build a bridge with the white bricks to keep Junkbot off the fire.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Use the pre-made stairs. Grab them from the bottom and move them into place.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Make a bridge to keep Junkbot off the bottom.  Watch the ceiling - Junkbot can't climb if there isn't room.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Make a stack of bricks behind the trashcan. Then build a roof that extends underneath the leaky pipes.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Make some stairs and then use them over again to get to the can in the opposite corner.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Jump bricks make Junkbot jump over walls and gaps. You can't move grey jump bricks.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Climbbots can go up and down walls. Use the yellow stairs to trap the climbbot underneath Junkbot.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: When Junkbot is in the air, putting bricks over the fan will bring him back down.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: The lower fan is tricky. Try building over from the stairs. Don't build too high or Junkbot won't have enough headroom.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Try making the Climbbots drop down to the lower level before you make a bridge for Junkbot.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Uncover the fans to give Junkbot a lift. Block the fans to make Junkbot drop.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: A central column can help to support the bridge across.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: If Junkbot can't go over the Gearbot, move the Gearbot instead.  Gearbots will roll over flat surfaces only.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Before you move a clump of bricks, think about where they'll go. You may have to dig Junkbot out one brick at a time.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: First build a lid to protect Junkbot from the Gearbots, and then build the plank to get Junkbot to the can.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Bots moving over a fan will cut off its breeze momentarily.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Getting the cans in the right order will help you save moves. Plan carefully.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: You can make a zig-zag stairway straight up from Junkbot. Add each new step just before Junkbot will climb it.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Open the door for the Climbbot on one side, and then climb up on the other.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Be sure Junkbot walks out a bit before you cut off the fan, or it will land right back on the old platform.  
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: The yellow jump brick can be moved. Use it to get Junkbot from platform to platform.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Start building from the center brick to reach both sides.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Let the Climbbots fall to the level above or below Junkbot and trap them there to safely build across.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Trap the flybots on the right to get the can on the left. Then trap them on the left and get the can on the right.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Block off the switch to keep the fires down.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Go under the bridge using the fans. Make a half bridge from one side and then move it to the other.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Remove and add walls to control where Junkbot lands.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: First build cover for Junkbot to get the first two cans.  Then  shuffle the cover around to get the remaining three.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: The fan you uncover should be the one closest to the can.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Build over the switches that are off, and not the ones that are on.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: If grey bricks are in Junkbot's way, you may have to come around from a different direction.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Get Junkbot to the lower platform, and then use the jumps to cross the gaps.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: The bottom switch doesn't do what you think! Build a bridge over the last fire.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Take each hazard as it comes; first protect Junkbot against the drip, and then look out for the Gearbot.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Starting with the head, break the monster down. Build a bridge that goes over the grey bricks above the eyebot.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Get the bottom can, and then use the fans to get the upper three.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Block the Eyebot, and then go for the can.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: The switches are past the fire, so make sure that Junkbot picks up a shield before you try to get the cans.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Remember: The shield only protects Junkbot once, so you have to protect him the second time.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Move as fast as you can, and keep bricks between you and the Eyebots!
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: It's all in the timing.  Figure out when the fire will be off, and then keep Junkbot away from the other switches.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: First trap the Eyebots, and then go after the cans.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Use both platforms to construct the bridges.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: The real switches are hidden among a number of false ones.  Find them and then turn them off.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: It's all in the timing. You'll have to use the jump brick more than once.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Turn off the top two switches first. Then use the fans to get around without turning them back on.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: You need to reach the switch to get to the can, so your first goal is to get a shield to take Junkbot past the drip.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Remove the upper bricks first to get Junkbot up the tunnel quickly.  Make sure the Eyebots don't slip in.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Trap the troublemakers in the lower right corner, and use the fan to help you on the way down.
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence

gameObjects.hint: Have fun making your own LEGO sculptures in the Art Factory!
gameObjects.name: LevelSequence
